value.0: A charming redhead, Sarah, leads the mage guard of Fort Cystana with vigor and expertise. Often found mingling among teacher and recruit alike, she bubbles with energy and always seems to be up to something.
Set into a copper band is a single green eye, constantly scanning the area and blinking now and then.  When the eye spots something, a faint tingle can be felt in the ring finger.

Julas of the Stoneguard Militia crafted this large shield from redwoods found in the Lonely Valley. The specially selected materials contained an innate magic that granted courage and willpower to the wielder.

A fine stringed instrument, a lute is very mobile, and as such, a favorite of traveling minstrels everywhere.  It has a pleasing sound, as the strings musical vibrations echo in the hollow wooden chamber and reverberate.
A percussion instrument, the tambourine is a colorful and playful musical device that is often used in dancing and keeping a rhythm.
A harp is a stringed instrument, which often produces dulcet gentle tones, assuming the person playing it has any talent for such things, of course.
